onal laws regulating intellectual property.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aBusiness intelligencezUnited StatesxHistory. 0aBusiness intelligence; United States; History. 0aIndustrial propertyzUnited StatesxHistory. 0aIndustrial property; United States; History. 0aPiracy (Copyright)zUnited StatesxHistory. 0aPiracy (Copyright); United States; History. 0aTechnological innovationszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aTechnological innovations; United States; History. 0aTrade secretszUnited StatesxHistory. 0aTrade secrets; United States; History. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economic History.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030012721840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300127218423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300127218/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles